title: $:/plugins/sq/window-resize/readme

@@color:red;''Experimental plugin - no support available. Use at your own risk.''@@

Updates the following info tiddlers with the window width and height on window resize:

* $:/info/browser/window/outer/width
* $:/info/browser/window/outer/height
* $:/info/browser/window/inner/width
* $:/info/browser/window/inner/height
* $:/info/browser/window/client/width
* $:/info/browser/window/client/height

Invokes actions in tiddlers tagged `$:/tags/WindowResizeAction` on window resize.